title: Steely Dan - 2006-08-12 - Live at Charlotte
description:
Such a sad occosion to share this with you... RIP Walter Becker, he will be missed.

Excellent stuff, really recommended. Artwork included. 

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

I use fast servers but also need your help, there's too much downloaders to handle.
